HitecAstro DC Focuser INDI driver install

Install your OS "build essentials" (gcc, binutils, etc).

Ensure you have followed the instructions to install INDI library following 
their instructions and additionally install libindi-dev packages.

Then...

1) cd ~
2) git clone https://github.com/A-j-K/hitecastrodcfocuser.git
3) mkdir -p ~/hitecastrodcfocuser/build
4) cd ~/hitecastrodcfocuser/build
5) cmake ..
6) make
7) sudo make install

